Anderson Hays Cooper -LRB- born June 3 , 1967 -RRB- is an American journalist , television personality , and author .
He is the primary anchor of the CNN news show Anderson Cooper 360 Â° .
The program is normally broadcast live from a New York City studio ; however , Cooper often broadcasts live from CNN 's studios in Washington , D.C. , or on location for breaking news stories .
In addition , he is a major correspondent for 60 Minutes .
From September 2011 to May 2013 , he also served as host of his own eponymous syndicated daytime talk show , Anderson Live .